She began going on auditions and met Nicole Kidman, who remains one of her closest friends, at one of them. She landed her first small film role when she was 18 and three years later appeared with Kidman in the film Flirting. She appeared with a young Russell Crowe in a TV mini-series, Brides of Christ and moved to America to try her luck in Hollywood when she was 24.
